# Only the licence-clean style encoder may enter the image. NDA-derived
# keypoint weights and the user's fine-tuned detector must never be baked in
# (defence in depth: HF builds from git where they are already absent, but a
# local `docker build` would otherwise copy the on-disk weights/).
weights/*
!weights/style_encoder.pt
